            inlineHelpText: DO NOT set this value unless you have discussed with LiveLabs team. LiveLabs Sandbox determines the tenancy.
            helpText:
                ```html
                DO NOT set this value unless you need to run this event on a very specific tenancy. <br><br>
                Selecting a tenancy can break the workshop if the tenancy does not have the correct resources in place. Please use this field with caution and only when you are certain you need it. 
                ```
        }
        comments {
            comments:
                ```
                -- server side condition
                select email from workshop_person_event_admin
                    where lower(email) = lower(:APP_USER)
                    and active_flg = 1
                UNION
                select user_name_lc
                    from APEX_APPL_ACL_USERS
                    where APPLICATION_ID = :APP_ID 
                    and role_names = 'Administrator'
                    and lower(user_name_lc) = lower(:APP_USER)
                ```
